    "Html": "<p>Just as a followup; storing the result of the XPath in an ObservableCollection worked just fine, but do I really need to go that extra step of converting from XML to POCO? &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"color:Black;background-color:White\">\r\n<pre>            XmlNodeList nodelist = xd.SelectNodes(<span style=\"color:#A31515\">&quot;//Stats/dataDist/DataCounts&quot;</span>);\r\n            <span style=\"color:Blue\">foreach</span> (XmlNode node <span style=\"color:Blue\">in</span> nodelist) {\r\n                Console.WriteLine(node.InnerText);\r\n                <span style=\"color:Blue\">double</span> d = 0;\r\n                <span style=\"color:Blue\">if</span> (<span style=\"color:Blue\">double</span>.TryParse(node.InnerText, <span style=\"color:Blue\">out</span> d))\r\n                    values.Add(d);\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            DataContext = values; <span style=\"color:#008000\">// values is ObservableCollection&lt;double&gt;</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Am I doing something wrong in hooking up the data to the chart, or is there no built in capability of setting the item source straight from XPath?</p>\r\n<pre style=\"font-size:1em;font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', Courier, monospace\"><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">d3</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">ColumnChart</span> <span style=\"color:red\">x:Name</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">chart</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:red\">ItemsSource</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">{Binding XPath=/Stats/dataDist/DataCounts}</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"font-size:1em;font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', Courier, monospace\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><br></span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"font-size:1em;font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', Courier, monospace\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">Thanks again for any help.</span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"font-size:1em;font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', Courier, monospace\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">E.</span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"font-size:1em;font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', Courier, monospace\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><br></span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"font-size:1em;font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', Courier, monospace\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><br></span></pre>",
